# Snyk
https://snyk.io/
https://github.com/snyk/snyk
https://hub.docker.com/r/snyk/snyk-cli

Develop fast.
Stay secure.
Enabling more than 400,000 developers to continuously find and fix vulnerabilities in open source libraries and containers.

## Using Snyk  
Please open https://snyk.io/ and sign up for a Free Account

![Snyk Sign Up](images/snyk-sign-up.png?raw=true "Snyk Sign Up")

Now just click Other or select where the code is

![Snyk Where is the Code](images/snyk-where-is-the-code.png?raw=true "Snyk Where is the Code")

Copy your SNYK_TOKEN and integrate into Snyk CLI

![Snyk Token](images/snyk-account-settings-api-token.png?raw=true "Snyk Token")

After the scan it will be available in your Snyk dashboard at: https://app.snyk.io/org/
![Snyk Dashboard](images/snyk-dashboard-projects.png?raw=true "Snyk Dashboard")

And the Full report is also available
![Snyk Dashboard](images/snyk-dashboard-projects-scan-report.png?raw=true "Snyk Dashboard")
